comments: Gordon (DEN) moves alongside Jones' (SAS) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Mamukelashvili (SAS) jumps alongside Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during the post shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim during the putback attempt.
Wembanyama (SAS) moves alongside of Jokic's (DEN) path to the basket and marginal arm contact occurs when Jokic lifts his arm upwards into Wembanyama's arm.
Mamukelashvili (SAS) cleanly blocks Porter Jr.'s (DEN) shot attempt near the rim.
Wembanyama (SAS) has his right arm extended outwards but he does not initiate illegal contact with Jokic (DEN) that causes him to lose control of the rebound.
Jones (SAS) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Porter Jr.'s (DEN) arm.
Champagnie (SAS) and Murray (DEN) both reach for the rebound and incidental arm contact occurs.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is moving alongside Wembanyama's (SAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the start of the drive.
Gordon (DEN) moves alongside Graham's (SAS) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Champagnie's (SAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jokic (DEN) brings his hands toward Graham (SAS) and marginal contact occurs as Jokic releases away to roll.
Graham (SAS) rests his hand on Jokic's (DEN) front after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) is retreating away from Graham (SAS) as he makes a move to the basket and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Murray (DEN) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
